name: Texnero
tagline: TexNero - A relaxing PC card game! To play, click the "DRAW" button. This will put random numbers on the buttons to the right. To win, you must have the same number on all 3 buttons.
body:
_Note: Java 8 or above needed._
### Downloads
* [Microsoft Windows](https://github.com/Kivitoe/TexNero/archive/master.zip)
